# --- Secrets ---
# .wp-credentials.env IS committed (private GH Enterprise repo only).
# Pre-push hook in .githooks/pre-push blocks pushing to any "Public-Sites" URL
# while credentials are present. Run: git config core.hooksPath .githooks
# on each clone to activate the hook.

